            <div class="small-12 columns">
                <div class="social-media-links UA_ShareModalLinks" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22Model%20and%20Method%20for%20Providing%20Resilience%20to%20Resource-Constrained%20AI-System&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/2955510%3A%0A%0AModel%20and%20Method%20for%20Providing%20Resilience%20to%20Resource-Constrained%20AI-System

Artificial%20intelligence%20technologies%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20prevalent%20in%20resource-constrained%2C%20safety-critical%20embedded%20systems.%20Numerous%20methods%20exist%20to%20enhance%20the%20resilience%20of%20AI%20systems%20against%20disruptive%20influences.%20However%2C%20when%20resources%20are%20limited%2C%20ensuring%20cost-effective%20resilience%20becomes%20crucial.%20A%20promising%20approach%20for%20reducing%20the%20resource%20consumption%20of%20AI%20systems%20during%20test-time%20involves%20applying%20the%20concepts%20and%20methods%20of%20dynamic%20neural%20networks.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20resilience%20of%20dynamic%20neural%20networks%20against%20various%20disturbances%20remains%20underexplored.%20This%20paper%20proposes%20a%20model%20architecture%20and%20training%20method%20that%20integrate%20dynamic%20neural%20networks%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20resilience.%20Compared%20to%20conventional%20training%20methods%2C%20the%20proposed%20approach%20yields%20a%2024%25%20increase%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20convolutional%20networks%20and%20a%2019.7%25%20increase%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20visual%20transformers%20under%20fault%20injections.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20results%20in%20a%2016.9%25%20increase%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20convolutional%20network%20ResNet-110%20and%20a%2021.6%25%20increase%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20visual%20transformer%20DeiT-S%20under%20adversarial%20attacks%2C%20while%20saving%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20computational%20resources.%20Meta-training%20the%20neural%20network%20model%20improves%20resilience%20to%20task%20changes%20by%20an%20average%20of%2022%25%2C%20while%20achieving%20the%20same[...]" title="Email">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-square" style="font-size: 30px;"></i>
                    </a>

                                        <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Model+and+Method+for+Providing+Resilience+to+Resource-Constrained+AI-System&amp;hashtags=mdpisensors&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2955510&amp;via=Sensors_MDPI" onclick="windowOpen(this.href,600,800); return false" title="Twitter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
